OL,3,CPep Guardiola gives 'fatty' warning as
OL,4,Che weighs Man City players over
OL,5,CChristmas
OL,7,FPep Guardiola has weighed his players
OL,8,Fand warned them not to over-indulge at
OL,9,FChristmas.
OL,11,FThe Manchester City manager has made
OL,12,Fclear that any member of the squad who
OL,13,Freturns from a short festive break out
OL,14,Fof condition will not be involved at
OL,15,FNottingham Forest next week.
OL,17,FGuardiola even refused his players a
OL,18,Fday off after Saturday's comfortable
OL,19,FPremier League victory over West Ham
OL,20,Fto make sure the message hit home.
