OL,3,CPep Guardiola gives 'fatty' warning as
OL,4,Che weighs Man City players over
OL,5,CChristmas
OL,7,FThe Spaniard was not happy with the
OL,8,Flevel of performance, even though the
OL,9,F3-0 success ` their fifth league
OL,10,Fvictory in succession ` kept the
OL,11,Fpressure on leaders Arsenal and even
OL,12,Ftook them top for a few hours.
OL,14,FGuardiola said: "The players asked me
OL,15,Fto take a day off. I said, 'No because
OL,16,Fyou didn't play good enough'.
OL,18,F"So Sunday recovery, train the guys
OL,19,Fthat didn't play, and after three days
OL,20,Foff they have two days to prepare for
OL,21,FNottingham Forest.
OL,26,@vD@QOUzD@AOU
