OL,3,CPep Guardiola gives 'fatty' warning as
OL,4,Che weighs Man City players over
OL,5,CChristmas
OL,7,F"Every player makes a weight. They
OL,8,Fcome back on the 25th and I will be
OL,9,Fthere controlling how many kilos come
OL,10,Fup, (to see if) they come fatty.
OL,12,F"The moment they arrive after three
OL,13,Fdays I want to see how they come back.
OL,14,FThey can eat but I want to control
OL,15,Fthem.
OL,17,F"I have to make a selection for 27
OL,18,F(December) against Nottingham Forest.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
