OL,3,CPep Guardiola gives 'fatty' warning as
OL,4,Che weighs Man City players over
OL,5,CChristmas
OL,7,F"Imagine one player and now he's
OL,8,Fperfect but he will arrive with three
OL,9,Fkilos more. He will (stay) in
OL,10,FManchester. He will not travel to
OL,11,FNottingham Forest."
OL,13,FGuardiola did point out that he
OL,14,Fcurrently saw "everything perfect" in
OL,15,Fterms of fitness, and it was other
OL,16,Faspects of the display against the
OL,17,FHammers that bothered him.
