OL,3,CPep Guardiola gives 'fatty' warning as
OL,4,Che weighs Man City players over
OL,5,CChristmas
OL,7,FHe said: "The problem is not running.
OL,8,FOne of the attributes of my teams
OL,9,Fsince I started in Barcelona B until
OL,10,Fnow is that we run like an animal, but
OL,11,Fit's not enough. We have to play
OL,12,Fbetter."
OL,14,FDespite that, Guardiola does feel it
OL,15,Fis important his players spend some
OL,16,Ftime with their families and enjoy
OL,17,Fthemselves.
OL,26,@oD@JOUtD@HO]
