OL,3,CPep Guardiola gives 'fatty' warning as
OL,4,Che weighs Man City players over
OL,5,CChristmas
OL,7,FIt is the first time since the
OL,8,FNovember international break that City
OL,9,Fhave not had a midweek fixture and he
OL,10,Fhimself is heading to Barcelona to
OL,11,Fspend time with his father.
OL,13,FHe said: "Next week I have holidays,
OL,14,Fbeing with family and with champagne.
OL,16,F"I've learned from England, since I
OL,17,Farrived, as much days (where you can)
OL,18,Fhave a day off, you give them.
OL,26,@uD@JOUxD@AOU
