OL,3,CPep Guardiola gives 'fatty' warning as
OL,4,Che weighs Man City players over
OL,5,CChristmas
OL,7,F"The schedule is so tight and the
OL,8,Fplayers have to forget. The more they
OL,9,Farrive in the right moment (the
OL,10,Fbetter). The moment of the game they
OL,11,Fwill be fresh in the legs.
OL,13,F"The players have to go with the
OL,14,Ffamilies and forget football. It's
OL,15,Fgood. For them to see the manager
OL,16,Fevery day ` that's so tough!"
